			<p style="margin-top: 35px; width: 270px;">
				<strong>What's Mingle?</strong><br /> It's the best agile tool for teams who refuse mediocrity. Be great. Work your way. Check out <a target="_blank" style="color:<%= mingle_color %>; text-decoration: none" href="http://www.thoughtworks.com/mingle">www.thoughtworks.com/mingle</a> or follow us on Twitter <a target="_blank" href="https://www.twitter.com/thatsmingle" style="color:<%= mingle_color %>; text-decoration: none">@thatsmingle</a>.
			</p>
	  </div>
	</center>
